//000000000000a:40:{s:2:"id";s:5:"28640";s:4:"body";s:218:"要求厨师从12种主料中挑选出2种、从13种配料中挑选出3种来烹饪某道菜肴，烹饪的方式共有7种，那么该厨师最多可以做出多少道不一样的菜肴?（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）";s:7:"bd_desc";s:0:"";s:7:"options";s:117:"[{"cs":"A ", "text":"131204"},{"cs":"B ", "text":"132132"},{"cs":"C ", "text":"130468"},{"cs":"D ", "text":"133456"}]";s:11:"description";s:908:"解法一：从12种主料中选出2种的方法数为&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/7fb0bf127a077c34e513215088b97d33_0.png" />，从13种配料中选出3种的方法数为&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/4ead912c48637507919479fd2e5f6869_1.png" />，从7种烹饪方式中选出1的方法数为&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/82d4503c60aa8658a5082792337930a4_2.png" />，因此总的方法数为&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/1f7d728e2875d830475fcc64bd75d55c_3.png" /> ，由尾数法可判断最后答案的尾数为2。因此，本题答案选择B选项。解法二：总的方法数为：&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/1f7d728e2875d830475fcc64bd75d55c_3.png" /> ，最后结果中显然含有“3”这个因子，而选项中只有B项满足。同样的，最终结果中会含有“7”这个因子，同样可以排除A、C、D三项。因此，本题正确答案为B。";s:7:"dp_desc";s:194:"7fb0bf127a077c34e513215088b97d33_0.png|4ead912c48637507919479fd2e5f6869_1.png|82d4503c60aa8658a5082792337930a4_2.png|1f7d728e2875d830475fcc64bd75d55c_3.png|1f7d728e2875d830475fcc64bd75d55c_4.png";s:6:"answer";s:1:"B";s:8:"wrongans";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:10:"optiontype";s:1:"1";s:8:"bigtype1";s:12:"数量关系";s:10:"smalltype1";N;s:10:"pointtype1";s:15:"分步计算型";s:5:"tagid";s:1:"0";s:6:"chance";s:1:"0";s:6:"ismock";s:1:"1";s:5:"qyear";s:4:"2009";s:5:"views";s:1:"0";s:6:"rorate";s:1:"0";s:7:"usetime";s:1:"0";s:10:"materialid";s:1:"0";s:4:"diff";s:1:"0";s:7:"addtime";s:1:"0";s:10:"updatetime";s:1:"0";s:10:"supplierid";s:1:"2";s:8:"sourceid";s:5:"55295";s:8:"insertid";s:1:"0";s:6:"extend";s:264:"<p class="item-p">一个数能被3整除，当且仅当其各位数字之和能被3整除。一个数能被7整除，当且仅当其末一位的两倍，与剩下的数之差为7的倍数；或者当且仅当其末三位数与剩下的数之差为7的倍数。</p>";s:5:"skill";s:49:"<p class="item-p">尾数法、数字特性法</p>";s:7:"bigtype";s:1:"2";s:9:"smalltype";s:1:"0";s:9:"pointtype";s:1:"0";s:6:"tagids";N;s:7:"errnums";s:1:"0";s:8:"collects";s:1:"0";s:5:"marks";s:1:"0";s:5:"notes";s:1:"0";s:4:"bugs";s:1:"0";s:7:"loglist";N;s:9:"pointname";N;}
